  "用 std::chrono 测出每帧耗时 dt（秒），并把 update 改成 update(World&, float dt)，让位移按 速度×dt 计算。": "Use std::chrono to measure each frame's elapsed dt (seconds), change update to update(World&, float dt), and compute displacement as speed × dt.",
  "用 std::chrono::steady_clock::now() 取两个时间点，相减得到时长；再用 std::chrono::duration<float>(now - last).count() 转成「秒」的浮点数。": "Take two timestamps with std::chrono::steady_clock::now(), subtract them, then convert to floating seconds with std::chrono::duration<float>(now - last).count().",
  "别用 system_clock 测帧间隔——它可能被系统对时往回跳。测时长一律用 steady_clock，它只会单调向前。": "Don't use system_clock to time frames — it can jump backward when the OS resyncs. For durations always use steady_clock, which only moves forward.",
